{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I grew up"},{"time":2000,"text":"in a very small village in Canada,"},{"time":5000,"text":"and I'm an undiagnosed"},{"time":8000,"text":"dyslexic."},{"time":10000,"text":"I had a really hard time in school."},{"time":13000,"text":"In fact, my mother told me eventually"},{"time":15000,"text":"that I was the little kid in the village"},{"time":17000,"text":"who cried all the way to school."},{"time":22000,"text":"I ran away."},{"time":24000,"text":"I left when I was 25 years old to go to Bali,"},{"time":29000,"text":"and there I met my incredible wife, Cynthia,"},{"time":32000,"text":"and together, over 20 years,"},{"time":35000,"text":"we built an amazing jewelry business."},{"time":38000,"text":"It was a fairy tale, and then we retired."},{"time":41000,"text":"Then she took me to see a film"},{"time":43000,"text":"that I really didn't want to see."},{"time":46000,"text":"It ruined my life --"},{"time":49000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":51000,"text":"\"The Inconvenient Truth\" and Mr. Gore."},{"time":54000,"text":"I have four kids,"},{"time":57000,"text":"and even if part of what he says is true,"},{"time":60000,"text":"they're not going to have the life that I had."},{"time":64000,"text":"And I decided at that moment"},{"time":67000,"text":"that I would spend the rest of my life"},{"time":70000,"text":"doing whatever I could"},{"time":73000,"text":"to improve their possibilities."},{"time":77000,"text":"So here's the world,"},{"time":79000,"text":"and here we are in Bali."},{"time":82000,"text":"It's a tiny, little island --"},{"time":84000,"text":"60 miles by 90 miles."},{"time":86000,"text":"It has an intact Hindu culture."},{"time":89000,"text":"Cynthia and I were there."},{"time":91000,"text":"We had had a wonderful life there,"},{"time":94000,"text":"and we decided to do something unusual."},{"time":97000,"text":"We decided to give back"},{"time":100000,"text":"locally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"And here it is: it's called the Green School."},{"time":105000,"text":"I know it doesn't look like a school,"},{"time":107000,"text":"but it is something we decided to do,"},{"time":110000,"text":"and it is extremely,"},{"time":112000,"text":"extremely green."},{"time":115000,"text":"The classrooms have no walls."},{"time":118000,"text":"The teacher is writing on a bamboo blackboard."},{"time":121000,"text":"The desks are not square."},{"time":124000,"text":"At Green School, the children are smiling --"},{"time":127000,"text":"an unusual thing for school, especially for me."},{"time":130000,"text":"And we practice holism."},{"time":133000,"text":"And for me it's just the idea"},{"time":135000,"text":"that, if this little girl"},{"time":137000,"text":"graduates as a whole person,"},{"time":139000,"text":"chances are"},{"time":141000,"text":"she'll demand a whole world --"},{"time":143000,"text":"a whole world --"},{"time":145000,"text":"to live on."},{"time":147000,"text":"Our children spend 181 days"},{"time":150000,"text":"going to school in a box."},{"time":153000,"text":"The people that built my school"},{"time":155000,"text":"also built the prison and the insane asylum"},{"time":158000,"text":"out of the same materials."},{"time":163000,"text":"So if this gentleman"},{"time":165000,"text":"had had a holistic education,"},{"time":167000,"text":"would he be sitting there?"},{"time":169000,"text":"Would he have had more possibilities in his life?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":174000,"text":"The classrooms have natural light."},{"time":176000,"text":"They're beautiful. They're bamboo."},{"time":179000,"text":"The breeze passes through them."},{"time":181000,"text":"And when the natural breeze isn't enough,"},{"time":184000,"text":"the kids deploy bubbles,"},{"time":186000,"text":"but not the kind of bubbles you know."},{"time":188000,"text":"These bubbles are made from natural cotton"},{"time":190000,"text":"and rubber from the rubber tree."},{"time":193000,"text":"So we basically turned the box"},{"time":195000,"text":"into a bubble."},{"time":197000,"text":"And these kids know"},{"time":199000,"text":"that painless climate control"},{"time":202000,"text":"may not be"},{"time":204000,"text":"part of their future."},{"time":207000,"text":"We pay the bill at the end of the month,"},{"time":209000,"text":"but the people that are really going to pay the bill"},{"time":211000,"text":"are our grandchildren."},{"time":214000,"text":"We have to teach the kids"},{"time":216000,"text":"that the world is not indestructible."},{"time":221000,"text":"These kids did a little graffiti on their desks,"},{"time":224000,"text":"and then they signed up for two extra courses."},{"time":227000,"text":"The first one was called sanding"},{"time":230000,"text":"and the second one was called re-waxing."},{"time":233000,"text":"But since that happened,"},{"time":236000,"text":"they own those desks."},{"time":239000,"text":"They know they can control their world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"We're on the grid. We're not proud of it."},{"time":246000,"text":"But an amazing alternative energy company in Paris"},{"time":249000,"text":"is taking us off the grid with solar."},{"time":252000,"text":"And this thing"},{"time":254000,"text":"is the second vortex to be built in the world,"},{"time":257000,"text":"in a two-and-a-half meter drop on a river."},{"time":260000,"text":"When the turbine drops in,"},{"time":262000,"text":"it will produce 8,000 watts of electricity,"},{"time":264000,"text":"day and night."},{"time":266000,"text":"And you know what these are."},{"time":268000,"text":"There's nowhere to flush."},{"time":270000,"text":"And as long as we're taking our waste"},{"time":272000,"text":"and mixing it with a huge amount of water --"},{"time":274000,"text":"you're all really smart, just do the math."},{"time":277000,"text":"How many people times how much water."},{"time":279000,"text":"There isn't enough water."},{"time":281000,"text":"These are compost toilets,"},{"time":283000,"text":"and nobody at the school wanted to know about them,"},{"time":286000,"text":"especially the principal."},{"time":289000,"text":"And they work. People use them. People are okay."},{"time":292000,"text":"It's something you should think about doing."},{"time":296000,"text":"Not many things didn't work."},{"time":299000,"text":"The beautiful canvas and rubber skylights"},{"time":302000,"text":"got eaten by the sun in six months."},{"time":304000,"text":"We had to replace them with recyclable plastic."},{"time":308000,"text":"The teachers dragged giant PVC whiteboards"},{"time":311000,"text":"into the classrooms."},{"time":313000,"text":"So we had some good ideas:"},{"time":315000,"text":"we took old automobile windshields, put paper behind them"},{"time":318000,"text":"and created the first alternative"},{"time":320000,"text":"to the whiteboard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324000,"text":"Green School sits in south-central Bali,"},{"time":327000,"text":"and it's on 20 acres"},{"time":329000,"text":"of rolling garden."},{"time":331000,"text":"There's an amazing river traveling through it,"},{"time":334000,"text":"and you can see there"},{"time":336000,"text":"how we manage to get across the river."},{"time":339000,"text":"I met a father the other day; he looked a little crazed."},{"time":342000,"text":"I said, \"Welcome to Green School.\""},{"time":344000,"text":"He said, \"I've been on an airplane for 24 hours.\""},{"time":348000,"text":"I asked him, \"Why?\""},{"time":351000,"text":"He said, \"I had a dream once about a green school,"},{"time":354000,"text":"and I saw a picture of this green school,"},{"time":356000,"text":"I got on an airplane."},{"time":358000,"text":"In August I'm bringing my sons.\""},{"time":361000,"text":"This was a great thing."},{"time":363000,"text":"But more than that,"},{"time":365000,"text":"people are building green houses around Green School,"},{"time":368000,"text":"so their kids can walk to school on the paths."},{"time":372000,"text":"And people are bringing their green industries,"},{"time":374000,"text":"hopefully their green restaurants,"},{"time":376000,"text":"to the Green School."},{"time":378000,"text":"It's becoming a community."},{"time":380000,"text":"It's becoming a green model."},{"time":383000,"text":"We had to look at everything."},{"time":385000,"text":"No petrochemicals in the pavement."},{"time":387000,"text":"No pavement."},{"time":389000,"text":"These are volcanic stones laid by hand."},{"time":391000,"text":"There are no sidewalks."},{"time":393000,"text":"The sidewalks are gravel. They flood when it rains,"},{"time":396000,"text":"but they're green."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398000,"text":"This is the school buffalo."},{"time":402000,"text":"He's planning to eat that fence for dinner."},{"time":405000,"text":"All the fences at Green School are green."},{"time":407000,"text":"And when the kindergarten kids"},{"time":409000,"text":"recently moved their gate,"},{"time":411000,"text":"they found out the fence was made out of tapioca."},{"time":414000,"text":"They took the tapioca roots up to the kitchen,"},{"time":417000,"text":"sliced them thinly and made delicious chips."},{"time":420000,"text":"Landscaping."},{"time":423000,"text":"We manage to keep the garden that was there"},{"time":425000,"text":"running right up to the edge of each of the classrooms."},{"time":428000,"text":"We dropped them gently in."},{"time":430000,"text":"We made space for these guys"},{"time":433000,"text":"who are Bali's last black pigs."},{"time":437000,"text":"And the school cow"},{"time":439000,"text":"is trying to figure out"},{"time":441000,"text":"how to replace the lawnmower"},{"time":443000,"text":"on the playing field."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445000,"text":"These young ladies"},{"time":447000,"text":"are living in a rice culture,"},{"time":449000,"text":"but they know something that few people know in a rice culture."},{"time":452000,"text":"They know how to plant organic rice,"},{"time":454000,"text":"they know how to look after it,"},{"time":456000,"text":"they know how to harvest and they know how to cook it."},{"time":459000,"text":"They're part of the rice cycle"},{"time":461000,"text":"and these skills will be valuable"},{"time":463000,"text":"for them in their future."},{"time":465000,"text":"This young man is picking organic vegetables."},{"time":469000,"text":"We feed 400 people lunch every day"},{"time":472000,"text":"and it's not a normal lunch. There's no gas."},{"time":475000,"text":"Local Balinese women"},{"time":477000,"text":"cook the food on sawdust burners"},{"time":480000,"text":"using secrets that only their grandmothers know."},{"time":484000,"text":"The food is incredible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":488000,"text":"Green School is a place of pioneers,"},{"time":490000,"text":"local and global."},{"time":492000,"text":"And it's a kind of microcosm"},{"time":494000,"text":"of the globalized world."},{"time":496000,"text":"The kids are from 25 countries."},{"time":498000,"text":"When I see them together,"},{"time":500000,"text":"I know that they're working out"},{"time":503000,"text":"how to live in the future."},{"time":506000,"text":"Green School is going into its third year"},{"time":508000,"text":"with 160 children."},{"time":510000,"text":"It's a school where you do learn reading --"},{"time":512000,"text":"one of my favorites --"},{"time":514000,"text":"writing -- I was bad at it --"},{"time":516000,"text":"arithmetic."},{"time":518000,"text":"But you also learn other things."},{"time":520000,"text":"You learn bamboo building."},{"time":522000,"text":"You practice"},{"time":524000,"text":"ancient Balinese arts."},{"time":526000,"text":"This is called mud wrestling in the rice fields."},{"time":529000,"text":"The kids love it."},{"time":531000,"text":"The mothers aren't quite convinced."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":535000,"text":"We've done a lot of outrageous things in our lives,"},{"time":537000,"text":"and we said, okay, local, what does \"local\" mean?"},{"time":540000,"text":"Local means"},{"time":542000,"text":"that 20 percent of the population of the school"},{"time":544000,"text":"has to be Balinese,"},{"time":546000,"text":"and this was a really big commitment."},{"time":548000,"text":"And we were right."},{"time":550000,"text":"And people are coming forward"},{"time":552000,"text":"from all over the world"},{"time":555000,"text":"to support the Balinese Scholarship Fund,"},{"time":558000,"text":"because these kids will be Bali's next green leaders."},{"time":562000,"text":"The teachers are as diverse"},{"time":564000,"text":"as the student body,"},{"time":566000,"text":"and the amazing thing"},{"time":568000,"text":"is that volunteers are popping up."},{"time":570000,"text":"A man came from Java"},{"time":572000,"text":"with a new kind of organic agriculture."},{"time":574000,"text":"A woman came from Africa with music."},{"time":577000,"text":"And together these volunteers and the teachers"},{"time":580000,"text":"are deeply committed"},{"time":582000,"text":"to creating a new generation"},{"time":584000,"text":"of global, green leaders."},{"time":588000,"text":"The Green School effect --"},{"time":590000,"text":"we don't know what it is."},{"time":592000,"text":"We need someone to come and study it."},{"time":594000,"text":"But what's happening, our learning-different kids --"},{"time":597000,"text":"dyslexic --"},{"time":599000,"text":"we've renamed them prolexic --"},{"time":602000,"text":"are doing well in these beautiful, beautiful classrooms."},{"time":606000,"text":"And all the kids are thriving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":609000,"text":"And how did we do all this?"},{"time":611000,"text":"On giant grass."},{"time":614000,"text":"It's bamboo."},{"time":616000,"text":"It comes out of the ground like a train."},{"time":619000,"text":"It grows as high as a coconut tree in two months"},{"time":623000,"text":"and three years later it can be harvested"},{"time":625000,"text":"to build buildings like this."},{"time":627000,"text":"It's as strong and dense as teak"},{"time":631000,"text":"and it will hold up any roof."},{"time":635000,"text":"When the architects came, they brought us these things,"},{"time":638000,"text":"and you've probably seen things like this."},{"time":640000,"text":"The yellow box was called the administration complex."},{"time":643000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":645000,"text":"We squashed it, we rethought it,"},{"time":648000,"text":"but mainly we renamed it"},{"time":651000,"text":"\"the heart of school,\""},{"time":653000,"text":"and that changed everything forever."},{"time":655000,"text":"It's a double helix."},{"time":657000,"text":"It has administrators in it"},{"time":659000,"text":"and many, many other things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":661000,"text":"And the problem of building it --"},{"time":663000,"text":"when the Balinese workers"},{"time":665000,"text":"saw long reams of plans,"},{"time":668000,"text":"they looked at them and said, \"What's this?\""},{"time":671000,"text":"So we built big models."},{"time":673000,"text":"We had them engineered by the engineers."},{"time":676000,"text":"And Balinese carpenters like this"},{"time":678000,"text":"measured them with their bamboo rulers,"},{"time":681000,"text":"selected the bamboo and built the buildings"},{"time":684000,"text":"using age-old techniques,"},{"time":687000,"text":"mostly by hand."},{"time":690000,"text":"It was chaos."},{"time":693000,"text":"And the Balinese carpenters want to be as modern as we do,"},{"time":696000,"text":"so they use metal scaffolding"},{"time":699000,"text":"to build the bamboo building"},{"time":702000,"text":"and when the scaffolding came down,"},{"time":707000,"text":"we realized that we had a cathedral,"},{"time":710000,"text":"a cathedral to green,"},{"time":712000,"text":"and a cathedral to green education."},{"time":715000,"text":"The heart of school has seven kilometers"},{"time":717000,"text":"of bamboo in it."},{"time":719000,"text":"From the time the foundations were finished,"},{"time":721000,"text":"in three months it had roofs and floors."},{"time":724000,"text":"It may not be the biggest bamboo building in the world,"},{"time":727000,"text":"but many people believe"},{"time":729000,"text":"that it's the most beautiful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732000,"text":"Is this doable in your community?"},{"time":735000,"text":"We believe it is."},{"time":737000,"text":"Green School is a model we built for the world."},{"time":740000,"text":"It's a model we built for Bali."},{"time":743000,"text":"And you just have to follow these simple, simple rules:"},{"time":746000,"text":"be local,"},{"time":748000,"text":"let the environment lead"},{"time":750000,"text":"and think about"},{"time":752000,"text":"how your grandchildren might build."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756000,"text":"So, Mr. Gore, thank you."},{"time":759000,"text":"You ruined my life,"},{"time":761000,"text":"but you gave me an incredible future."},{"time":764000,"text":"And if you're interested in being involved"},{"time":766000,"text":"in finishing Green School"},{"time":769000,"text":"and building the next 50 around the world,"},{"time":771000,"text":"please come and see us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":773000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":775000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}